        <isViewedAsPlainText>false</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Cloud-1 Task Reminder&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Dear &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;{!$Record.Owner:User.FirstName}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;I hope this email finds you well. I am writing to remind you about the upcoming task with a due date of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;{!$Record.ActivityDate}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;, which is tomorrow. As a friendly reminder, tomorrow will be the last day to complete this task.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Task Details:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Subject&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;{!$Record.Subject}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;{!$Record.Description}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Due Date&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;{!$Record.ActivityDate}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Please ensure that you allocate the necessary time and resources to complete the task by the specified deadline. If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to reach out to me.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Your prompt attention to this matter is greatly appreciated. Thank you for your cooperation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Regards,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cloud-1 Management.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;ï»¿&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cloud146-dev-ed.develop.file.force.com/sfc/dist/version/renditionDownload?rendition=ORIGINAL_Png&amp;amp;versionId=0685g00000I7Wxz&amp;amp;operationContext=DELIVERY&amp;amp;contentId=05T5g000010jKy7&amp;amp;page=0&amp;amp;d=/a/5g000000p6tl/pPiMPCuKqyGtEg_Yrx.wj5mIJ67sM007h7qskQgWUsM&amp;amp;oid=00D5g00000KgNe5&amp;amp;dpt=null&amp;amp;viewId=&quot; alt=&quot;logoblack.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
